article_id:1676,category_name:News,title_name:Summon Showcase: Dragon Special Is Now Live!,image_path:,message:<div>The Summon Showcase: Dragon Special kicked off at <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1602482400"></span>!</div><div><br></div><div>The appearance rates for featured 4★ and 5★ dragons are currently boosted.</div><div><br></div><div>Dragon Special appearance rates:</div><div>5★ featured - Total: 2.40% (Adventurers: 0%, Dragons: 2.40%)</div><div>5★ normal - Total: 1.60% (Adventurers: 0.75%, Dragons: 0.85%)</div><div>4★ featured - Total: 7.00% (Adventurers: 0%, Dragons: 7.00%)</div><div>4★ normal - Total: 9.00% (Adventurers: 5.05%, Dragons: 3.95%)</div><div>3★ normal - Total: 80.00% (Adventurers: 48.00%, Dragons: 32.00%)</div><div><br></div><div>This showcase will be available from <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1602482400"></span> to <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1602827999"></span>.</div><div><br></div><div>Get a closer look at the featured dragons below.</div><div><br></div><div>Featured Dragons:</div><div>
