	<div class="title">Abilities</div>
	<dl><dt><span><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/7ea00c46aa6b565d6054e18deab891fa2.png"></span><span>(Wind) Summer Flowers V</span></dt><dd><div>If the user is attuned to Wind:<br>grants the user a "Smiling Flower" at the start<br>of quests, and grants an additional Smiling Flower<br>every 60 seconds, up to a maximum of six.<br>The user will receive the following buffs based<br>on their total number of Smiling Flowers.<br>One Flower: Increases strength by 40%<br>Two Flowers: Increases defense by 20%<br>Three Flowers: Increases skill damage by 50%<br>Four Flowers: Reduces water damage taken by 5%<br>Six Flowers: Grants an HP regen buff</div></dd></dl></div></div></div><div><br></div><div>
